data.description: Step into a wonderful blend of space and comfort with this fantastic 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home! The spacious open floor plan downstairs is a breath of fresh air, providing the ideal area for entertaining family and friends. The large bonus room located downstairs can be utilized for a home office or a playroom! Perched in the highly desirable Tulare south east neighborhood you're sure to love. Park with ease in the 3 car garage, ensuring convenience for all of your vehicles. Beyond the walls, enjoy all the outdoor space in the great backyard with a covered patio. Come see for yourself what this move-in ready home offers.
